<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ạ̹ḥnạ lyk sẖkl fynạ jml bạ̹ydyk ạ̉wạnynạ
 wḥd qlbnạ bklạmk jsd wạḥd fy ạ̉ḥḍạnk
 ạlqrạr- yạ sẖạmlnạ bạ̹ḥsạnk yạlly sbytnạ bjmạlk
 bnqdm lk ạ̉rwạḥnạ wạ̹ḥnạ yạ rb wlạdk
 2- yạmạ snyn mrt bynạ wkạsryn ʿhdnạ fynạ
 jyt bḥbk tjmʿnạ wạlḥq mnwr lynạ
 3- ʿlmtnạ ạ̹zạy ngẖfr wạ̹nt ạlgẖạfr mʿạṣynạ
 gẖfrạnk dh mạlwsẖ ḥd ṭwlh mạ byn ạlsmạ wạlạ̉rḍ
 4- ʿlmtnạ ạ̹zạy nzrʿ wḥṣạdnạ yrjʿ lynạ
 njmʿ bwfrẗ ḥyạẗ ạ̉fḍl ṭwl mạ ạ̹nt fynạ</lyrics>
<title>sẖkl fynạ</title>
</song>